# Netflix Clone Implementation Plan

**Goal**: Create a fully responsive, animated, black-and-white themed streaming platform with a robust admin backend and internal CMS, using TMDB for metadata and Rivestream for playback.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Hosting Constraints**: The project is designed for shared hosting (PHP/MySQL). I will assume a standard MySQL database is available. For local development, I will use SQLite (`db/database.sqlite`) to demonstrate functionality without needing a local MySQL server setup. You can switch to MySQL in `api/config.php` by changing the `DB_CONNECTION` setting.

> [!NOTE]
> **Rivestream API**: The embed URL pattern will be configured in `api/config.php`. I will use a standard pattern initially, which you can update if the documentation requires a specific format I couldn't auto-detect.

